### Listar Todos os Usuários
GET {{baseUrl}}/usuarios
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected Response
# Status: 200 OK
# {
#   "data": [...],
#   "total": 50,
#   "page": 1,
#   "limit": 10,
#   "totalPages": 5
# }

###

### Listar com Paginação
GET {{baseUrl}}/usuarios?page=2&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected Response
# Status: 200 OK
# {
#   "data": [...],
#   "total": 50,
#   "page": 2,
#   "limit": 20,
#   "totalPages": 3
# }

###

### Filtrar por Nome
GET {{baseUrl}}/usuarios?nome=João
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected Response
# Status: 200 OK
# {
#   "data": [
#     {
#       "id": "uuid",
#       "nomeCompleto": "João da Silva",
#       ...
#     }
#   ],
#   "total": 5,
#   "page": 1,
#   "limit": 10,
#   "totalPages": 1
# }

###

### Filtrar por Email
GET {{baseUrl}}/usuarios?email=joao
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Filtrar por CPF
GET {{baseUrl}}/usuarios?cpf=12345678901
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Filtrar por Status Ativo
GET {{baseUrl}}/usuarios?ativo=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Filtrar por Unidade
GET {{baseUrl}}/usuarios?unidadeId=uuid-unidade-1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Filtros Combinados
GET {{baseUrl}}/usuarios?ativo=true&unidadeId=uuid-unidade-1&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected Response
# Status: 200 OK
# {
#   "data": [...],
#   "total": 15,
#   "page": 1,
#   "limit": 20,
#   "totalPages": 1
# }